meta.name: Capital Jingle Bell Ball
meta.description: Highlights of the pop concert held at London's O2.

videos.overview: Jordan North, Chris Stark and Sian Welby present highlights of the Christmas party at London's O2. Featuring performances by a star-studded line-up including Ed Sheeran, Kylie Minogue, RAYE, Louis Tomlinson, Alex Warren, Jessie J, Leigh-Anne, Tinie Tempah and Anne-Marie, and a special KPop Demon Hunters sing-along.
